iMy various servers host different services, each with its own		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iusername/password system, making unified management difficult. If my		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ipassword were compromised in the future, changing them individually		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iwould be extremely tedious. Therefore, I want to use a dedicated		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
